tic seizures.', 'Synergism', 'The use of opioids in conjunction with benzodiazepines or other CNS depressants should generally be avoided unless alternative treatment options are inadequate.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/300830/', '', 'Naltrexone, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Dihydrocodeine, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 'Nitrazepam, Zopiclone', 1767369485);
